🍋 LEMON Restaurant Menu

A modern and colorful restaurant menu website built using 
HTML and CSS. This project focuses on creating an attractive
and user-friendly dining experience with a clean layout,
vibrant lemon-inspired theme, and responsive design.

🚀 Features

- Modern Lemon Theme UI
- Responsive Design
- Interactive Menu Sections
- Starters, Main Course, and Desserts Categories
- Order Online Card
- Reserve Table Card
- Smooth Hover Effects
- Clean and Easy Navigation

🛠️ Technologies Used

- HTML5
- CSS3

