🎨 Theme

The website uses a bright yellow and orange 
color palette inspired by fresh lemons to create 
a vibrant and welcoming restaurant atmosphere.

📱 Responsive Design

The layout is optimized for:

- Desktop
- Tablet
- Mobile Devices

